reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars great quality & price!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. this was extremely easy to put together (no more than 10min), came with written & picture instructions.the quality exceeded my expectations & the fabric bin is very sturdy and spacious.it has a little stop in the back of the cabinet to keep the bin from sliding out the back & comes with stickers to cover the screws as well (my kids took them off though hahah)very pleased with this item! i wasn't wanting to spend too much on a piece of furniture for my toddler son so I wasn't expecting to be able to find a nightstand that was affordable, but also nice looking & good quality. highly recommend!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars High Quality, Good Price, And Very Sturdy. Highly Recommend!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This nightstand was very easy to put together. I would say I built it in about 10-20 minutes. It is very sturdy, and is a very good size. Has enough room for my alarm clock, lamp, books, ETC. The drawer is large, and very suitable for my, and most peoples needs. I am very positively surprised and impressed by the workmanship and quality of this nightstand. Especially for the price! It was only like $40! Which is a slightly below reasonable price but many nightstands are like 70 or 80 for the same quality and looks!Thank you,B. W.
